[
    {
        "source_sentence": "大般涅槃經集解卷第三十五",
        "translation": "Mahāparinirvāṇa-sūtra, Collected and Explained, Volume 35",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a06_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　釋從佛出十二部經從十二部經出脩多羅從脩多羅出方等經從方等經出波若從波若出涅槃義出菩薩在雪山為半偈捨身緣起聖行品之第九爾時眾中有一菩薩(至)阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "translation": "From the Buddha came twelve scriptures, from the twelve scriptures came sūtra, from sūtra came vaipulya, from vaipulya came prajñā, from prajñā came nirvāṇa, and from the meaning of prajñā came the ninth chapter of the Noble Actions Chapter in which a bodhisattva renounces the body in half a verse on Mount Snow.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a08_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a14_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧亮曰。",
        "translation": "Sengliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a14_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此經明復說經功德。",
        "translation": "\"This sūtra explains the merit of repeating the sūtra.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a14_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "勸人行經。",
        "translation": "It encourages people to practice the sūtras.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a14_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "經即法也。",
        "translation": "The sūtras are the Dharma.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a15_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行法雖由人。",
        "translation": "Although it's up to people to practice the Dharma, it's up to them to cease evil.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a15_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然滅惡由法也。",
        "translation": "It's up to the person to practice the Dharma, but it's up to the Dharma to cease evil.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a15_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬藥能治病。",
        "translation": "It's like medicine that can treat a disease.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a15_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖由人能服。",
        "translation": "Although it's up to people to take it, the power to remove illness lies in the medicine.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a16_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然去病之力在藥也。",
        "translation": "The medicine has the power to remove the disease.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a16_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是以法華經云。",
        "translation": "That's why the Lotus Sutra says.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a16_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若罵佛者。",
        "translation": "\"If someone ridicules the Buddha.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a17_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人罪輕。",
        "translation": "That person's sin is minor.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a17_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毀經法者。",
        "translation": "Someone who disparages the sūtras and the Dharma has a heavy sin.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a17_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "罪則重也。",
        "translation": "That's a serious offense.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a18_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寶亮曰。",
        "translation": "Baoliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a18_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此下第四段歎經流通也。",
        "translation": "\"This is the fourth paragraph below, which praises the circulation of the sūtras.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a18_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有四翻。",
        "translation": "There are four versions of it.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a19_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第一無垢藏王歎。",
        "translation": "The first is the lamentation of the king of the stainless store.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a19_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第二佛自歎。",
        "translation": "Second, the Buddha praises himself.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a19_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第三迦葉歎。",
        "translation": "The third is Kāśyapa's praise.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a19_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第四佛引證。",
        "translation": "The fourth is when the Buddha cites it as proof.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a20_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "成迦葉所歎也。",
        "translation": "It's the accomplishment of Kāśyapa's lamentation.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a20_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此即第一無垢王歎。",
        "translation": "This is the first praise of the king of stainless steel.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a20_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時佛讚言善哉善哉(至)無量無邊不可稱計。",
        "translation": "The Buddha then praised him, saying, \"Good, good!\" (to) \"Measureless and limitless! Incalculable!",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a22_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a23_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧亮曰。",
        "translation": "Sengliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a23_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛教從小起。",
        "translation": "\"The Buddha's teaching starts with the small.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a23_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "牛譬佛也。",
        "translation": "The cow is a metaphor for the Buddha.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a23_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乳譬三藏。",
        "translation": "Milk is an example of the Tripiṭaka.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a23_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "酪譬三乘雜說也。",
        "translation": "Milk is like the Tripiṭaka, and cheese is like the Tripiṭaka's mixed teachings.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a24_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生蘇譬方等。",
        "translation": "Raw sow is an example of equality in terms of direction.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a24_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "熟蘇譬說空般若。",
        "translation": "Ripe soap meets the prajñāpāramitā of teaching emptiness.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a24_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "醍醐譬涅槃經法也。",
        "translation": "Daigo likens it to the teaching of the Nirvana sutra.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a25_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "法難見者。",
        "translation": "\"It's difficult to see the Dharma.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a25_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "空有也。",
        "translation": "It's emptiness and existence.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a25_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以般若說空。",
        "translation": "Prajñāpāramitā teaches emptiness ...",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a26_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "涅槃說有也。",
        "translation": "Nirvāṇa teaches about existence.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a26_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛難見涅槃。",
        "translation": "It's difficult for the Buddha to see nirvāṇa.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a26_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為勝尊重讚歎也。",
        "translation": "It's a great honor and praise.'",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a26_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧宗曰。",
        "translation": "The Saṃgha School said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a27_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聖行所以而成功。",
        "translation": "\"This is the reason the noble practice succeeds.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a27_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由經力。",
        "translation": "It's because of the power of the sūtras.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a27_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生人圓解也。",
        "translation": "It gives rise to the perfect understanding of people.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a28_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如從牛出乳者。",
        "translation": "He's like someone who gives birth to milk from a cow.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a28_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說小乘四諦法輪。",
        "translation": "The Buddha taught the Dharma wheel of the four lesser vehicle truths.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a28_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此是成佛十二年中說也。",
        "translation": "This was said twelve years after becoming a buddha.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a29_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從乳出酪者。",
        "translation": "\"From milk comes cream.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493a29_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂十二年後。",
        "translation": "It's twelve years later.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b01_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "說三乘通教。",
        "translation": "He taught the common teaching of the three vehicles.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b01_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大品經是也。",
        "translation": "This is the scripture of the Great Vehicle.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b01_25",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "酪出生蘇者。",
        "translation": "\"From the milk comes Su.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b02_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如思益維摩。",
        "translation": "It's like Suye Vimalakīrti.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b02_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "抑挫二乘。",
        "translation": "He suppresses the two vehicles and praises the bodhisattvas.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b02_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "稱揚菩薩也。",
        "translation": "It's called praising the bodhisattvas.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b02_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從生蘇出熟蘇者。",
        "translation": "He who produces ripened sesame from raw sesame.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b03_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "說法花破無三因果也。",
        "translation": "It's called the flower of the Dharma that refutes the absence of three causes and effects.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b03_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今此經明佛性常住。",
        "translation": "Now, this sūtra explains that the buddha nature is eternally abiding.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b04_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "窮理盡性。",
        "translation": "It exhausts the principle and nature.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b04_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如醍醐也。",
        "translation": "He's like ghee.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b04_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又出十二部者。",
        "translation": "\"Also, out of the twelve divisions comes this one.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b05_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "小乘十二部也。",
        "translation": "They're the twelve divisions of the lesser vehicle.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b05_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從十二部出脩多羅者。",
        "translation": "From the twelve divisions comes out Shūtāra.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b05_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "空教脩多羅也。",
        "translation": "It's the teaching of emptiness and sūtra.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b06_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但言脩多羅者。",
        "translation": "He only says sūtra.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b06_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "攝十二部故。",
        "translation": "It's because it includes the twelve divisions.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b06_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但言本耳。",
        "translation": "He only refers to the origin.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b07_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "出方等理正不耶。",
        "translation": "Does it not follow that the principle of the way out is correct?",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b07_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二乘等學般若。",
        "translation": "The two vehicles and others train in prajñā.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b07_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故以通教。",
        "translation": "Therefore, they use the shared teaching.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b08_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為方等也。",
        "translation": "It's also the same in every direction.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b08_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "出般若者。",
        "translation": "\"He who goes beyond prajñā.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b08_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一乘實慧般若也。",
        "translation": "It's the One Vehicle's true wisdom prajñā.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b08_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從般若出大涅槃者。",
        "translation": "He who produces great nirvāṇa from prajñā.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b09_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即今教也。",
        "translation": "This is the present teaching.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b09_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又一解云。",
        "translation": "Another explanation says.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b10_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此經文小誤。",
        "translation": "This is a minor error in the text of the sūtra.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b10_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若應為第三。",
        "translation": "\"Prajñā should be the third ...",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b10_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "方等應在第四也。",
        "translation": "He should have been fourth in terms of methods and so forth.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b10_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寶亮曰。",
        "translation": "Baoliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b11_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛如牛也。",
        "translation": "\"The Buddha is like a cow.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b11_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五味譬五時教也。",
        "translation": "The five flavors are a metaphor for the five teaching periods.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b11_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛初出世。",
        "translation": "The Buddha first appeared in the world.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b12_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十二年中。",
        "translation": "During the twelve years, he taught the lesser vehicle tripiṭaka.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b12_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "小乘三藏。",
        "translation": "The lesser vehicle Tripiṭaka.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b12_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "別相說法輪。",
        "translation": "They explained the wheel of the Dharma in a distinct way.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b12_25",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "置出世之教。",
        "translation": "This is called the setting aside of the teaching that comes out of this world.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b13_26",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "始當十二部之名也。",
        "translation": "It's the first to be called the twelve schools.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b13_27",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從十二年後。",
        "translation": "From the twelve years afterward.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b13_28",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "通教門中。",
        "translation": "In the general teaching, there's a teaching that discerns emptiness and existence.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b14_29",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "辨空有。",
        "translation": "It discerns emptiness and existence.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b14_30",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "明真俗二諦。",
        "translation": "It clarifies the two truths of true and secular.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b14_31",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "理既深廣。",
        "translation": "As the principle becomes deep and broad, it's like milk coming out of cheese.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b14_32",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如從乳出酪。",
        "translation": "It's like milk coming out of cheese.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b15_33",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二諦是空解之主。",
        "translation": "The two truths are the lords of understanding emptiness and the roots of all understanding.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b15_34",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦是萬解之本。",
        "translation": "They're also the root of all understanding.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b15_35",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以當脩多羅名也。",
        "translation": "That's why they should be called sūtra.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b16_36",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但自通教之前。",
        "translation": "But it was before the Shared Teaching.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b16_37",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "直明因果。",
        "translation": "It was a straightforward explanation of cause and effect.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b17_38",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "義不辨二諦。",
        "translation": "The meaning didn't discern the two truths.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b17_39",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "忘相故不與本之稱。",
        "translation": "Because it forgets characteristics, it's not called the origin.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b17_40",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從脩多羅出方等經者。",
        "translation": "\"From Śuddhodana came the scripture of equality in terms of direction.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b18_41",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自通教說後。",
        "translation": "It's been taught since the time of the Shared Teaching.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b18_42",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "述維摩思益。",
        "translation": "He recounted Vimalakīrti's benefits.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b18_43",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "進聲聞行。",
        "translation": "He advanced the practice of the śrāvakas.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b19_44",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "令捨執得解。",
        "translation": "He causes them to abandon their attachments and attain understanding.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b19_45",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故以方等經。",
        "translation": "That's why he uses the vaipulya sūtras.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b19_46",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如從酪出生蘇也。",
        "translation": "'It's like producing soap from cream.'",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b20_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從方等出般若波羅蜜者。",
        "translation": "\"From this formula comes prajñā-pāramitā. Prajñā means wisdom.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b20_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若言智慧。",
        "translation": "Prajñā means wisdom.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b21_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從說維摩。",
        "translation": "It's derived from the teaching Vimalakīrti.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b21_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "後明法花。",
        "translation": "It's followed by the teaching of the flower of the Dharma.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b21_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "辨一因一果。",
        "translation": "It identifies one cause and one effect.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b21_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "智慧開明。",
        "translation": "It's enlightened by wisdom.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b22_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以譬般若。",
        "translation": "This is an analogy for Prajñā.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b22_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "喻之熟蘇也。",
        "translation": "It's a metaphor for ripening sentient beings.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b22_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既說法花經竟。",
        "translation": "After explaining the Dharma Flower Sutra, he finished.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b22_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "涅槃教與明理具足。",
        "translation": "\"The teaching of nirvāṇa and the clarification of principle are complete.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b23_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶若醍醐也。",
        "translation": "It's like ghee.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b23_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉菩薩白佛言世尊(至)恭敬供養尊重讚歎。",
        "translation": "Kāśyapa said to the Buddha, \"Bhagavān,\" (to) respectfully offer support, honor, and praise him.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b25_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b26_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧宗曰。",
        "translation": "The Saṃgha School said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b26_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉是請法之主。",
        "translation": "\"Kāśyapa is the one who invites the teaching.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b26_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自說修行之相。",
        "translation": "He himself explains the features of his practice.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b26_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "法瑤曰。",
        "translation": "Fayao said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b27_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "上來雖明聖行。",
        "translation": "\"Although the Bhagavān explained the noble conduct of the above, he didn't exhaust its beauty.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b27_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "未盡其美。",
        "translation": "They didn't exhaust their merits.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b27_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此章廣明慕法情重。",
        "translation": "This chapter explains in detail how deeply he admires the Dharma.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b27_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "捨其身命。",
        "translation": "They abandon their bodies and lives.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b28_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不以為難。",
        "translation": "It doesn't take it as a hardship.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b28_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以此捨心修習聖行往不備。",
        "translation": "With this kind of renunciation, cultivating noble behavior will never be complete.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b28_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以此苦行。",
        "translation": "With this kind of asceticism, why would he go backwards?",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b29_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何往而退。",
        "translation": "How could he go backwards?",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b29_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聖行之難莫過於此。",
        "translation": "Nothing is more difficult for the noble practice than this.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493b29_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故以斯行。",
        "translation": "Therefore, this practice is the conclusion of the noble practice.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c01_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "結聖行之終矣。",
        "translation": "It's the conclusion of the noble practice.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c01_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時佛讚迦葉菩薩(至)諸行無常是生滅法。",
        "translation": "It was then that the Buddha praised Kāśyapa Bodhisattva (to) that the impermanence of conditioned phenomena is the law of arising and ceasing.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c02_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c03_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "智宗曰。",
        "translation": "The School of Wisdom says.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c03_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先說無常也。",
        "translation": "\"First, we'll talk about impermanence.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c03_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以二理必對必應圓說。",
        "translation": "It's explained in the round because the two principles must be matched and should be matched.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c03_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故謂半如意珠也。",
        "translation": "Therefore, it's called the half-rule of the wish-granting pearl.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c04_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "說是半偈已便住其前(至)生滅滅已寂滅為樂。",
        "translation": "After speaking this half-verse, he then abides in front of it (until) birth and extinction and then tranquility and cessation are enjoyable.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c05_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "智秀曰。",
        "translation": "Zhixiu said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c06_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "說常也。",
        "translation": "'It's said to be permanent.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c06_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寂滅無苦。",
        "translation": "'Tranquility is without suffering.'",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c06_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以無苦故。",
        "translation": "It's because there's no suffering.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c06_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名之為樂。",
        "translation": "It's called bliss.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c06_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無更別樂。",
        "translation": "There's no more distinct pleasure.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c07_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故云寂滅。",
        "translation": "That's why it's called tranquility.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c07_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時羅剎說是偈已(至)大般涅槃修於聖行。",
        "translation": "It was then that Rāṣṭrapāla spoke this verse and cultivated noble practices in the great parinirvāṇa.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c08_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c09_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧宗曰。",
        "translation": "The Saṃgha School said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c09_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "上已讚其所行為難。",
        "translation": "\"The above has already praised what he did as difficult.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c09_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今引昔事。",
        "translation": "Now, I'll cite past events.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c09_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以證護法之不虛。",
        "translation": "It's to prove that protecting the Dharma isn't in vain.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c09_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "求法之至也。",
        "translation": "It's also the ultimate in seeking the Dharma.",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c10_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大般涅槃經集解卷第三十五",
        "translation": "Collection and Understanding of the Sutra of the Great Decease, Volume 35",
        "source": "T37n1763_035:0493c11_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    }
]